title: ghost rider 5 for peter
description:
Plot Line:
Ghostrider is back! This time he is more extreme then          
ever, more police chases and hardcore riding.                                                                                
There are more police chases in this movie then ever           
before, insane car chases with GIS (Ghostrider in Subaru)      
and the whole police force in Stockholm including a            
helicopter, High Speed Challenge throughout Stockolm,          
Murder Attempt on Ghostrider by the Swedish Police,            
Uppsala Run - The Way Back Home, Supermotofun and much         
much more.
